IntelliJ IDEA 2019.3.5 is here! It brings a variety of updates and bug fixes. We've fixed the regression that caused v2019.3.4 not to start when installed in a path with non-ASCII characters: IDEA-235754. The IDE now shows the confirmation dialog when deleting a directory which is under SVN: IDEA-228828. The Gradle daemon no longer starts with debugging enabled when debugging tests and delegating to Gradle: IDEA-235648. The JBR has been updated to v11.0.6+8-b520.66. For more details please refer to the blog post.
